def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a = list(reversed(a))
    b = []
    for i in range(n):
        if a[i] not in b:
            b.append(a[i])
    b = list(reversed(b))
    print(len(b))
    print(" ".join(map(str, b)))

main()

def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    a_set = set(a)
    a_set = list(a_set)
    a_set.sort(key=lambda x: a.index(x), reverse=True)
    print(len(a_set))
    print(" ".join([str(x) for x in a_set]))

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    print(len(set(a)))
    print(*sorted(set(a), reverse=True))
    
if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
